high_descs: Turn to the right to face the toaster.
Pick up the fork from the far back edge of the counter.
Hold the fork and turn to around, then the left to locate the sink.
Place the fork in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off  Pick up the fork from the sink.
Carry the fork and take a few steps left to locate the small black table.
Place the fork on the right front side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a fork and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Turn right and head to the sink.
Put the fork in the sink, rinse it and pick it back up.
Turn around, turn right towards the table, turn right and go to the black table.
Put the fork on the table to the right of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed fork on the black table.

high_descs: Take a step forward then turn right.
Pick up the fork that's in front of you above the toaster.
Turn around and walk to the sink that's on your left.
Wash the fork in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Take a step to your left to face the black table then take a small step backwards.
Put the fork on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork on the table.
